      "content": "but he's really insistent that he's just dehydrated and jet lagged. he doesn't want to go to the hospital and make a scene or deal with all the paperwork if it's nothing. he's even asking if maybe some electrolytes and a long nap would help him feel better by morning. are u sure it's not just the travel stress?",
