    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but he's really stubborn lol. if i dont want to call an ambulance right this second, can you just tell me what else might be causing this so i can calm him down? like is there any other reason his arm would feel heavy after a long flight? i just want to be sure before i panic and call 911 for something that might just be a cramp or something.",
